  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give Hope to a Child with Sickle Cell Anaemia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project involve awareness campaign in senior secondary schools in Nigeria - visiting both private and public secondary schools educating and increasing awareness on heamoglobin compatibility between two people in order to reducing the rate of sickle cell anaemia victims in our society.The project shares pain management and other information useful in managing Sickle Cell Anaemia (SCA) through SMS. And also connect unaware Sickle Cell Anaemia patients from the rural villages with the clinic.</narrative>
  </description>
